fivbvis 0.0.6
  • Reference

    Return the fields for a given VIS data type

    v_fields.Rd

    Return the fields for a given VIS data type

    v_fields(type)

    Arguments

    type

    string: the data type, currently one of "Volleyball Tournament", "Volleyball Tournament Filter", "Volleyball Tournament Ranking", "Volleyball Match", "Volleyball Match Filter", "Volleyball Pool", "Volleyball Pool Filter", "Volleyball Pool Ranking", "Volleyball Team", "Volleyball Team Filter", "Volleyball Player", "Volleyball Player Filter", "Volleyball Player Ranking", "Volleyball Statistics"

    Value

    A character vector of field names

    References

    https://www.fivb.org/VisSDK/VisWebService/

    v_fields("Volleyball Tournament")
